{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/petal-before-and-after","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>This is a collection of tactical, small design wins, a sort of journal. <br> Looking for a robust case study? <a href=\"/blog/nubank/nuconta\">Try here.</a></h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><img src=\"/df5c778cb5589b41a2411456d7c8ea90/filters-before.gif\"></th>\n<th><img src=\"/013f1acd5aa547601ae3afd85b13aebb/filters-after-3.gif\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Before</strong></td>\n<td><strong>After ✓</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Customer support and usability testing revealed that users had trouble filtering important content that was two clicks away.</td>\n<td>By exposing the filter labels, users don’t need to guess what’s inside the dropdown. <a href=\"https://share.getcloudapp.com/wbu05LEA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Engagement increased ~500%.</em></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 130.88888888888889%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"bankLinking before\"\n        title=\"bankLinking before\"\n        src=\"/static/6fd07d77323a28b7cb17e1450a4515cc/d61c2/bankLinking-before.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6fd07d77323a28b7cb17e1450a4515cc/fc2a6/bankLinking-before.png 450w,\n/static/6fd07d77323a28b7cb17e1450a4515cc/1cfc2/bankLinking-before.png 900w,\n/static/6fd07d77323a28b7cb17e1450a4515cc/d61c2/bankLinking-before.png 1800w,\n/static/6fd07d77323a28b7cb17e1450a4515cc/b2313/bankLinking-before.png 2700w,\n/static/6fd07d77323a28b7cb17e1450a4515cc/75ac7/bankLinking-before.png 3600w,\n/static/6fd07d77323a28b7cb17e1450a4515cc/d7097/bankLinking-before.png 3608w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 130.88888888888889%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"bankLinking after\"\n        title=\"bankLinking after\"\n        src=\"/static/cc9b8e2794732a692c1707cd1a835f17/d61c2/bankLinking-after.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cc9b8e2794732a692c1707cd1a835f17/fc2a6/bankLinking-after.png 450w,\n/static/cc9b8e2794732a692c1707cd1a835f17/1cfc2/bankLinking-after.png 900w,\n/static/cc9b8e2794732a692c1707cd1a835f17/d61c2/bankLinking-after.png 1800w,\n/static/cc9b8e2794732a692c1707cd1a835f17/b2313/bankLinking-after.png 2700w,\n/static/cc9b8e2794732a692c1707cd1a835f17/75ac7/bankLinking-after.png 3600w,\n/static/cc9b8e2794732a692c1707cd1a835f17/d7097/bankLinking-after.png 3608w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Before</strong></td>\n<td><strong>After ✓</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Highest point of friction for Petal users is linking their accounts.</td>\n<td>By AB testing many hypothesis, we achieved a version that <a href=\"https://share.getcloudapp.com/p9u7Y00X\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>converts 117% more</em></a> than the initial design.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.77777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"feedItems before\"\n        title=\"feedItems before\"\n        src=\"/static/7bb654d2fd2ecfefdae75c0b4dc5ec6c/d61c2/feedItems-before.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7bb654d2fd2ecfefdae75c0b4dc5ec6c/fc2a6/feedItems-before.png 450w,\n/static/7bb654d2fd2ecfefdae75c0b4dc5ec6c/1cfc2/feedItems-before.png 900w,\n/static/7bb654d2fd2ecfefdae75c0b4dc5ec6c/d61c2/feedItems-before.png 1800w,\n/static/7bb654d2fd2ecfefdae75c0b4dc5ec6c/b2313/feedItems-before.png 2700w,\n/static/7bb654d2fd2ecfefdae75c0b4dc5ec6c/75ac7/feedItems-before.png 3600w,\n/static/7bb654d2fd2ecfefdae75c0b4dc5ec6c/d7097/feedItems-before.png 3608w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.77777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"feedItems after\"\n        title=\"feedItems after\"\n        src=\"/static/4667ba86d0286594c15fe24a227830de/d61c2/feedItems-after.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4667ba86d0286594c15fe24a227830de/fc2a6/feedItems-after.png 450w,\n/static/4667ba86d0286594c15fe24a227830de/1cfc2/feedItems-after.png 900w,\n/static/4667ba86d0286594c15fe24a227830de/d61c2/feedItems-after.png 1800w,\n/static/4667ba86d0286594c15fe24a227830de/b2313/feedItems-after.png 2700w,\n/static/4667ba86d0286594c15fe24a227830de/75ac7/feedItems-after.png 3600w,\n/static/4667ba86d0286594c15fe24a227830de/d7097/feedItems-after.png 3608w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Before</strong></td>\n<td><strong>After ✓</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Merchants were named with the raw strings we received, and category icons were assigned.</td>\n<td>With some quick Regex, we’re able to clean up names and display curated logos for +50% of purchases.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 95.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"desktop before\"\n        title=\"desktop before\"\n        src=\"/static/828a8baa6b2188f43bc9e4aa471d18a9/d61c2/desktop-before.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/828a8baa6b2188f43bc9e4aa471d18a9/fc2a6/desktop-before.png 450w,\n/static/828a8baa6b2188f43bc9e4aa471d18a9/1cfc2/desktop-before.png 900w,\n/static/828a8baa6b2188f43bc9e4aa471d18a9/d61c2/desktop-before.png 1800w,\n/static/828a8baa6b2188f43bc9e4aa471d18a9/b2313/desktop-before.png 2700w,\n/static/828a8baa6b2188f43bc9e4aa471d18a9/75ac7/desktop-before.png 3600w,\n/static/828a8baa6b2188f43bc9e4aa471d18a9/43068/desktop-before.png 9631w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 95.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"desktop after\"\n        title=\"desktop after\"\n        src=\"/static/7b1d00606719eb8bf5e2e3d711b4608b/d61c2/desktop-after.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7b1d00606719eb8bf5e2e3d711b4608b/fc2a6/desktop-after.png 450w,\n/static/7b1d00606719eb8bf5e2e3d711b4608b/1cfc2/desktop-after.png 900w,\n/static/7b1d00606719eb8bf5e2e3d711b4608b/d61c2/desktop-after.png 1800w,\n/static/7b1d00606719eb8bf5e2e3d711b4608b/b2313/desktop-after.png 2700w,\n/static/7b1d00606719eb8bf5e2e3d711b4608b/75ac7/desktop-after.png 3600w,\n/static/7b1d00606719eb8bf5e2e3d711b4608b/43068/desktop-after.png 9631w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Before</strong></td>\n<td><strong>After ✓</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Our desktop app was left aside for a while, missing some important navigation and styling alignments with the mobile app</td>\n<td>Unified design allowed more consistent, accessible experience, shared components and simpler code.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><img src=\"/885bfa818ecf8c5899579177d8097ba4/modals-before-12.gif\"></th>\n<th><img src=\"/9f2f4acb719394a5fad0581ff83a598e/modals-after-12.gif\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Before</strong></td>\n<td><strong>After ✓</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Initial modals had CTA and dismiss actions too close to each other and taking too much space. Centered rendering also becomes a problem as out phones grow taller and taller.</td>\n<td>Better distributed buttons allows for extra actions such as navigation and secondary CTAs and are more ergonomic on tall devices.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.22222222222222%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"toast before\"\n        title=\"toast before\"\n        src=\"/static/e5b87f02756ee3cf1b842e1c1b8108dd/d61c2/toast-before.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e5b87f02756ee3cf1b842e1c1b8108dd/fc2a6/toast-before.png 450w,\n/static/e5b87f02756ee3cf1b842e1c1b8108dd/1cfc2/toast-before.png 900w,\n/static/e5b87f02756ee3cf1b842e1c1b8108dd/d61c2/toast-before.png 1800w,\n/static/e5b87f02756ee3cf1b842e1c1b8108dd/b2313/toast-before.png 2700w,\n/static/e5b87f02756ee3cf1b842e1c1b8108dd/75ac7/toast-before.png 3600w,\n/static/e5b87f02756ee3cf1b842e1c1b8108dd/d7097/toast-before.png 3608w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.44444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"toast after\"\n        title=\"toast after\"\n        src=\"/static/c90e8687133019d690f932b99e48c416/d61c2/toast-after.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c90e8687133019d690f932b99e48c416/fc2a6/toast-after.png 450w,\n/static/c90e8687133019d690f932b99e48c416/1cfc2/toast-after.png 900w,\n/static/c90e8687133019d690f932b99e48c416/d61c2/toast-after.png 1800w,\n/static/c90e8687133019d690f932b99e48c416/b2313/toast-after.png 2700w,\n/static/c90e8687133019d690f932b99e48c416/75ac7/toast-after.png 3600w,\n/static/c90e8687133019d690f932b99e48c416/d7097/toast-after.png 3608w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Before</strong></td>\n<td><strong>After ✓</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Quite a few of Petal’s initial designs didn’t meet color contrast guidelines.</td>\n<td>It’s a daily battle towards better legibility!</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 115.77777777777779%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"light fonts before\"\n        title=\"light fonts before\"\n        src=\"/static/2213d05c91cea148c4cf2f2f7831b616/d61c2/light-fonts-before.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2213d05c91cea148c4cf2f2f7831b616/fc2a6/light-fonts-before.png 450w,\n/static/2213d05c91cea148c4cf2f2f7831b616/1cfc2/light-fonts-before.png 900w,\n/static/2213d05c91cea148c4cf2f2f7831b616/d61c2/light-fonts-before.png 1800w,\n/static/2213d05c91cea148c4cf2f2f7831b616/b2313/light-fonts-before.png 2700w,\n/static/2213d05c91cea148c4cf2f2f7831b616/75ac7/light-fonts-before.png 3600w,\n/static/2213d05c91cea148c4cf2f2f7831b616/3dd05/light-fonts-before.png 3800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 115.77777777777779%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"light fonts after\"\n        title=\"light fonts after\"\n        src=\"/static/6b902caeebea8ac923e6a39f7e925e0e/d61c2/light-fonts-after.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6b902caeebea8ac923e6a39f7e925e0e/fc2a6/light-fonts-after.png 450w,\n/static/6b902caeebea8ac923e6a39f7e925e0e/1cfc2/light-fonts-after.png 900w,\n/static/6b902caeebea8ac923e6a39f7e925e0e/d61c2/light-fonts-after.png 1800w,\n/static/6b902caeebea8ac923e6a39f7e925e0e/b2313/light-fonts-after.png 2700w,\n/static/6b902caeebea8ac923e6a39f7e925e0e/75ac7/light-fonts-after.png 3600w,\n/static/6b902caeebea8ac923e6a39f7e925e0e/3dd05/light-fonts-after.png 3800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Before</strong></td>\n<td><strong>After ✓</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Thin, light-gray fonts were great to get Petal hyped for its “designer look”.</td>\n<td>We banned light fonts and low-contrast text even from legal disclaimers. Going from light to regular goes a long way for legibility.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 142.88888888888889%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"navigation before 2\"\n        title=\"navigation before 2\"\n        src=\"/static/09b1d164150c42da4d07a54da98b3686/d61c2/navigation-before-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/09b1d164150c42da4d07a54da98b3686/fc2a6/navigation-before-2.png 450w,\n/static/09b1d164150c42da4d07a54da98b3686/1cfc2/navigation-before-2.png 900w,\n/static/09b1d164150c42da4d07a54da98b3686/d61c2/navigation-before-2.png 1800w,\n/static/09b1d164150c42da4d07a54da98b3686/b2313/navigation-before-2.png 2700w,\n/static/09b1d164150c42da4d07a54da98b3686/75ac7/navigation-before-2.png 3600w,\n/static/09b1d164150c42da4d07a54da98b3686/3dd05/navigation-before-2.png 3800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 142.88888888888889%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"navigation after 2\"\n        title=\"navigation after 2\"\n        src=\"/static/29b4d67f1d323c9a1f00414e6a9daea3/d61c2/navigation-after-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/29b4d67f1d323c9a1f00414e6a9daea3/fc2a6/navigation-after-2.png 450w,\n/static/29b4d67f1d323c9a1f00414e6a9daea3/1cfc2/navigation-after-2.png 900w,\n/static/29b4d67f1d323c9a1f00414e6a9daea3/d61c2/navigation-after-2.png 1800w,\n/static/29b4d67f1d323c9a1f00414e6a9daea3/b2313/navigation-after-2.png 2700w,\n/static/29b4d67f1d323c9a1f00414e6a9daea3/75ac7/navigation-after-2.png 3600w,\n/static/29b4d67f1d323c9a1f00414e6a9daea3/3dd05/navigation-after-2.png 3800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Before</strong></td>\n<td><strong>After ✓</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>As our app grew, our minimalist navigation starter to get too cryptic. Users relied on trial and error to find the desired content.</td>\n<td>Some Information Architecture gymnastics will soon enable us to achieve a much more understandable “home” for your money.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1800px;\"\n    >